    {
      "name": "Offset",
      "summary": "<p>其默认距离为百分之百，代表坐标轴标签之间以及标签与坐标轴线之间的默认距离。其值可以为从 0 到 1000 之间的一个整数百分比，表示相对于坐标轴标签的字号。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表各级别标签之间的距离以及第一级标签与坐标轴之间的距离。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*如果偏移量小于 500，则此示例将 Chart1 中分类轴上标签之间的距离设置为当前距离的两倍。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tickLabels = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Axes</span>(xlCategory).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TickLabels</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (tickLabels.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Offset</span> &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">500</span>) {\n        tickLabels.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Offset</span> = tickLabels.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Offset</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例显示 Sheet1 上的第一个图表数值轴刻度线标签之间的距离。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tickLabels = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Axes</span>(xlValue).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TickLabels</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(tickLabels.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Offset</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Orientation",
      "summary": "<p>此属性值可设为 -90 到 90 度之间的整数值或 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlTickLabelOrientation 枚举.html\">XlTickLabelOrientation</a></strong> 常量之一。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表文本方向。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例将 Chart1 上数值轴的刻度线标签的文本方向设置为向下排列。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tickLabels = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Axes</span>(xlValue).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TickLabels</span>\n    tickLabels.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Orientation</span> = xlTickLabelOrientationDownward\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例显示 Sheet1 上的第一个图表分类轴刻度线标签的文本方向是否由 ET 设置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tickLabels = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Axes</span>(xlCategory).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TickLabels</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(tickLabels.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Orientation</span> == xlTickLabelOrientationAutomatic)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlTickLabelOrientation",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
